background.user_prompt_template:
User description: "{user_description}"
Appearance JSON: {appearance_json}

Return a single JSON object with this structure:
{
  "brief_introduction": string,
  "background_story": string,
  "background_segments": [
    {"title": string, "content": string}
  ]
}
Rules:
- background_story should be 2-3 sentences.
- background_segments should be 2-4 items with concise titles and story beats.

personality_skills.user_prompt_template:
User description: "{user_description}"
Appearance JSON: {appearance_json}
Background JSON: {background_json}

Return a single JSON object with this structure:
{
  "personality_tags": string[],
  "extended_attributes": {"key": "value"},
  "greeting": string[],
  "quotes": string[],
  "skills": {
    "stats": [
      {"label": "STR", "value": number},
      {"label": "INT", "value": number},
      {"label": "AGI", "value": number},
      {"label": "VIT", "value": number},
      {"label": "DEX", "value": number},
      {"label": "LUK", "value": number}
    ],
    "abilities": [
      {"name": string, "type": "Default"|"Magic"|"Elemental"|"Physical"|"Psychic"|"Spatial"|"Buff"|"Summoning"|"Shapeshifting"|"Technological"|"Potion"|"Unique", "level": number, "description": string, "icon": "Default"|"Magic"|"Elemental"|"Physical"|"Psychic"|"Spatial"|"Buff"|"Summoning"|"Shapeshifting"|"Technological"|"Potion"|"Unique"}
    ]
  }
}
Rules:
- personality_tags should be 3-8 unique items.
- greeting should be an array of exactly 3 different greeting phrases, each reflecting the character's personality and how they would introduce themselves in a chat.
- quotes should be 2-3 short lines.
- stats values are integers from 1 to 10.
- abilities should be 3-5 items with distinct names.
- abilities[].type must be one of: Default, Magic, Elemental, Physical, Psychic, Spatial, Buff, Summoning, Shapeshifting, Technological, Potion, Unique.
- abilities[].icon must match abilities[].type and use the same value.
- abilities[].level should be an integer from 1 to 5.
